This is an implementation of the Kingdom O' Magic engine using the ScummVM
infrastructure.

To use:
* Apply scummvm-kom.patch to the scummvm root
* Copy the files in this repository to scummvm/engines/kom/

Please contact me if you want to help:
oavtal@bezeqint.net
or
salty-horse @ irc://freenode.net/scummvm


------------------------------------------------------------

This is a darcs repository.
It allows you to easily fetch the latest changes, make changes of your own, and
send them as patches via email.

To check-out the repository, run:
$ darcs get http://ori.codemongers.com/repos/kom

To get the latest changes, run:
$ darcs pull

For more information, visit http://darcs.net
